You can simply ask Alexa to control your Friedrich air conditioner. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our FriedrichGo app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our FriedrichGo app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app, then click on "Enable to Use" on this page.;
(4). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

* Alexa, turn on the Friedrich air conditioner
* Alexa, turn off Friedrich the air conditioner
* Alexa, set Friedrich air conditioner temperature to 27 degrees
* Alexa, increase Friedrich air conditioner temperature
* Alexa, decrease Friedrich air conditioner temperature
* Alexa, what’s the temperature of Friedrich air conditioner
